            <div class="questions">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <div class="innerContent ">

                    <h4 class="h4">
                      What is FA?
                    </h4>
                    <p>
                      FA is a rare, progressive disease that damages the nervous system, causing you to lose control of
                      your muscles over time.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <div class="innerContent ">
                    <h4 class="h4">
                      What causes FA?
                    </h4>
                    <p>
                      FA happens when a specific gene, called the frataxin gene (or FXN), does not function properly and
                      cannot help nerve cells work the way they should.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <div class="innerContent ">


                    <h4 class="h4">
                      How is FA diagnosed?
                    </h4>
                    <p>
                      FA can be confirmed with a genetic test. It is important that the test include a Friedreich
                      Ataxia
                      Repeat Expansion Analysis.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h4 class="h4">
              What happens as FA progresses?
            </h4>
            <p>
              As you get older, FA continues to damage nerve cells, which leads to greater difficulty with things like:
            </p>
            <ul class="symptomsList">
              <li>
                <div class="card ">
                  <div class="cardHeader">
                    <h5 class="h5">Standing</h5>
                  </div>
                  <div class="cardContent">
                    <img src="{{ base_path ~ directory }}/images/dtc/standing.svg" alt="standing">
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li>
                <div class="card ">
                  <div class="cardHeader">
                    <h5 class="h5">Walking</h5>
                  </div>
                  <div class="cardContent">
                    <img src="{{ base_path ~ directory }}/images/dtc/walking.svg" alt="walking">
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li>
                <div class="card ">
                  <div class="cardHeader">
                    <h5 class="h5">Talking</h5>
                  </div>
                  <div class="cardContent">
                    <img src="{{ base_path ~ directory }}/images/dtc/talking.svg" alt="talking">
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li>
                <div class="card ">
                  <div class="cardHeader">
                    <h5 class="h5">Fine motor skills</h5>
                  </div>
                  <div class="cardContent">
                    <img src="{{ base_path ~ directory }}/images/dtc/skills.svg" alt="skills">
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
